OL,3,CZero hours contracts restriction among
OL,4,Cproposals to strengthen workers' rights
OL,6,FRestrictions on zero hours contracts
OL,7,Fand the introduction of paid carers'
OL,8,Fleave are among proposals included in
OL,9,Fa plan to strengthen employment rights
OL,10,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FEconomy Minister Conor Murphy launched
OL,13,Fa public consultation exercise on a
OL,14,Fseries of measures linked to his Good
OL,15,FJobs strategy.
OL,17,FThe proposals also include giving
OL,18,Fworkers the right to request flexible
OL,19,Fworking arrangements from the first
OL,20,Fday of their employment.
