OL,3,CZero hours contracts restriction among
OL,4,Cproposals to strengthen workers' rights
OL,6,FThere is also a proposal to ban the
OL,7,Fpractice of "fire and rehire", where
OL,8,Femployees are let go and then rehired
OL,9,Fon reduced terms and conditions.
OL,11,FThe consultation also includes steps
OL,12,Fto make it easier for trade unions to
OL,13,Forganise in workplaces in Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FA right to disconnect from work out of
OL,17,Fhours has also been proposed, and a
OL,18,Fmeasure that would ensure tips to
OL,19,Fstaff are fully allocated to them by
OL,20,Ftheir companies.
