OL,3,CZero hours contracts restriction among
OL,4,Cproposals to strengthen workers' rights
OL,6,FThere are also proposals to make it
OL,7,Feasier for employers and worker to
OL,8,Fcalculate holiday pay.
OL,10,FThe consultation on legislative
OL,11,Fchanges also proposes giving workers
OL,12,Fthe right to take one week of unpaid
OL,13,Fleave a year for caring
OL,14,Fresponsibilities.
OL,16,FMr Murphy said it was also his "goal"
OL,17,Fto ensure carers could receive paid
OL,18,Fleave.
