OL,6,FHe said the introduction of a
OL,7,Fstatutory payment to support carers
OL,8,Ftaking leave would potentially cost
OL,9,Fthe Stormont Executive #60 million per
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe minister's plan also includes
OL,13,Fadditional statutory leave for working
OL,14,Fparents whose newborn children require
OL,15,Fneo-natal care.
