OL,6,F"This is an ambitious programme of
OL,7,Fwork," said Mr Murphy. "I will
OL,8,Fcontinue to consult with business and
OL,9,Ftrade union representatives to design
OL,10,Fa framework that operates effectively
OL,11,Ffor businesses, for workers and for
OL,12,Four economy.
OL,14,F"I encourage everyone to respond to
OL,15,Fthe consultation."
OL,17,FThe consultation will be open for 13
OL,18,Fweeks from July 1 2024 to September 30
OL,19,F2024.
